$$
\begin{align*}
\vec{u}_1^\top \vec{u}_2 &amp;= \alpha \beta - \alpha \beta = 0, \\
\vec{u}_2^\top \vec{u}_3 &amp;= -\beta \gamma + \beta \gamma = 0, \\
\vec{u}_1^\top \vec{u}_3 &amp;= -\alpha \gamma + 2\alpha \gamma - \alpha \gamma = 0.
\end{align*}
$$

取$U = (u_1,u_2,u_3)$, 有

$$
\begin{align*}
U^T M U &amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha &amp; \sqrt{2} \alpha &amp; \alpha \\
\beta &amp; 0 &amp; -\beta \\
-\gamma &amp; \sqrt{2} \gamma &amp; -\gamma
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
m &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; m &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; m
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha &amp; \beta &amp; -\gamma \\
\sqrt{2} \alpha &amp; 0 &amp; \sqrt{2} \gamma \\
\alpha &amp; -\beta &amp; -\gamma
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
4m \alpha^2 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 2m \beta^2 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 4m \gamma^2
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= I
\end{align*}
$$

需要取

$$\alpha = \pm \frac{1}{{2\sqrt m }},\beta = \pm \frac{1}{{\sqrt {2m} }},\gamma = \pm \frac{1}{{2\sqrt m }}$$

另一方面

$$
\begin{align*}
U^T K U &amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha &amp; \sqrt{2} \alpha &amp; \alpha \\
\beta &amp; 0 &amp; -\beta \\
-\gamma &amp; \sqrt{2} \gamma &amp; -\gamma
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
2k &amp; -k &amp; 0 \\
-k &amp; 2k &amp; -k \\
0 &amp; -k &amp; 2k
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha &amp; \beta &amp; -\gamma \\
\sqrt{2} \alpha &amp; 0 &amp; \sqrt{2} \gamma \\
\alpha &amp; -\beta &amp; -\gamma
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
(8 - 4\sqrt{2}) \alpha^2 k &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 4 \beta^2 k &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; (8 + 4\sqrt{2}) \gamma^2 k
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m} &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; \frac{2k}{m} &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; \frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= \Lambda
\end{align*}
$$

此时有

$$
\begin{cases}
\vec{u}_1 &amp;= \begin{pmatrix} \frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \\ \frac{1}{\sqrt{2m}} \\ \frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \end{pmatrix} \\
\vec{u}_2 &amp;= \begin{pmatrix} \frac{1}{\sqrt{2m}} \\ 0 \\ -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2m}} \end{pmatrix} \\
\vec{u}_3 &amp;= \begin{pmatrix} -\frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \\ \frac{1}{\sqrt{2m}} \\ -\frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \end{pmatrix}
\end{cases}
$$"><p>逐一验证</p><p></p><div class="MathJax" display="block" style="text-align:center;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="29.255ex" height="9.063ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 $$M\ddot {\vec y} + K \vec y = 0$$

有

$$MU\ddot {\vec \eta} + KU\vec \eta = 0$$

左乘$U^T$

$${U^T}MU\ddot {\vec \eta} + {U^T}KU\vec \eta = I\ddot {\vec \eta} + \Lambda \vec \eta = 0$$

即

$$
\begin{align*}
\ddot{\eta}_1 + \lambda_1 \eta_1 &amp;= 0, \\
\ddot{\eta}_2 + \lambda_2 \eta_2 &amp;= 0, \\
\ddot{\eta}_3 + \lambda_3 \eta_3 &amp;= 0.
\end{align*}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 &amp;= C_1 \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) + C_2 \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right), \\
\eta_2 &amp;= C_3 \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right) + C_4 \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right), \\
\eta_3 &amp;= C_5 \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) + C_6 \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right).
\end{cases}
$$"><p>令<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="6.985ex" height="2.4ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -845 3087.6 1061" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" $$U^TMU = I \Rightarrow U^{-1} = U^T M$$

有

$$
\begin{cases}
\begin{align*}
\vec{\eta}(0) &amp;= U^{-1} \vec{y}(0)\\
&amp;=U^T M \vec{y}(0) \\
&amp;= \frac{\sqrt{m}}{2} 
\begin{pmatrix}
1 &amp; \sqrt{2} &amp; 1 \\
\sqrt{2} &amp; 0 &amp; -\sqrt{2} \\
-1 &amp; \sqrt{2} &amp; -1
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
1 \\
0
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;=
\begin{pmatrix}
\sqrt{\frac{m}{2}} \\
0 \\
\sqrt{\frac{m}{2}}
\end{pmatrix} \\
\end{align*} \\
\dot{\vec{\eta}}(0) = U^T M \dot{\vec{y}}(0) = \vec{0}
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$${C_2} = {C_3} = {C_4} = {C_6} = 0,{C_1} = {C_5} = \sqrt {\frac{m}{2}}$$

所以

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 = \sqrt{\frac{m}{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\
\eta_2 = 0 \\
\eta_3 = \sqrt{\frac{m}{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right)
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$$
\begin{pmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{pmatrix} = 
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\
\frac{1}{2} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) + \frac{1}{2} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\
-\frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right)
\end{pmatrix}

\begin{cases}
\vec{\eta}(0) &amp;= U^T M \vec{y}(0) = \frac{\sqrt{m}}{2} 
\begin{pmatrix}
1 &amp; \sqrt{2} &amp; 1 \\
\sqrt{2} &amp; 0 &amp; -\sqrt{2} \\
-1 &amp; \sqrt{2} &amp; -1
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
-1 \\
0 \\
1
\end{pmatrix} = 
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
-\sqrt{2m} \\
0
\end{pmatrix} \\
\dot{\vec{\eta}}(0) &amp;= U^T M \dot{\vec{y}}(0) = \vec{0}
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$${C_3} = - \sqrt {2m} ,{C_1} = {C_2} = {C_4} = {C_5} = {C_6} = 0$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 = 0 \\
\eta_2 = - \sqrt{2m} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right)0 \\
\eta_3 = 0
\end{cases}
$$

\begin{pmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{pmatrix} = 
\begin{pmatrix}
-\cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right) \\
0 \\
\cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right)
\end{pmatrix}

\begin{cases}
\vec{\eta}(0) &amp;= U^T M \vec{y}(0) = \vec{0}, \\
\dot{\vec{\eta}}(0) &amp;= U^T M \dot{\vec{y}}(0) = \frac{\sqrt{m}}{2} 
\begin{pmatrix}
1 &amp; \sqrt{2} &amp; 1 \\
\sqrt{2} &amp; 0 &amp; -\sqrt{2} \\
-1 &amp; \sqrt{2} &amp; -1
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
1
\end{pmatrix} = 
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{\sqrt{m}}{2} \\
-\sqrt{\frac{m}{2}} \\
-\frac{\sqrt{m}}{2}
\end{pmatrix}.
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$${C_1} = {C_3} = {C_5} = 0,{C_2} = \frac{m}{{2\sqrt {\left( {2 - \sqrt 2 } \right)k} }},{C_4} = - \frac{m}{{2\sqrt k }},{C_6} = - \frac{m}{{2\sqrt {\left( {2 + \sqrt 2 } \right)k} }}$$

所以

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 &amp;= \frac{m}{2\sqrt{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\
\eta_2 &amp;= -\frac{m}{2\sqrt{k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right) \\
\eta_3 &amp;= -\frac{m}{2\sqrt{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right)
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$$
\begin{align*}
\begin{pmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{pmatrix} = 
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{1}{4}\sqrt{\frac{m}{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{1}{2}\sqrt{\frac{m}{2k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right) + \frac{1}{4}\sqrt{\frac{m}{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\
\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{\frac{m}{(4 - 2\sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{1}{2}\sqrt{\frac{m}{(4 + 2\sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\
\frac{1}{4}\sqrt{\frac{m}{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) + \frac{1}{2}\sqrt{\frac{m}{2k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right) + \frac{1}{4}\sqrt{\frac{m}{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right)
\end{pmatrix}
\end{align*}

div.data-content:
逐一验证

$$
\begin{align*}
\vec{u}_1^\top \vec{u}_2 &= \alpha \beta - \alpha \beta = 0, \\
\vec{u}_2^\top \vec{u}_3 &= -\beta \gamma + \beta \gamma = 0, \\
\vec{u}_1^\top \vec{u}_3 &= -\alpha \gamma + 2\alpha \gamma - \alpha \gamma = 0.
\end{align*}
$$

取$U = (u_1,u_2,u_3)$, 有

$$
\begin{align*}
U^T M U &=
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha & \sqrt{2} \alpha & \alpha \\
\beta & 0 & -\beta \\
-\gamma & \sqrt{2} \gamma & -\gamma
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
m & 0 & 0 \\
0 & m & 0 \\
0 & 0 & m
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha & \beta & -\gamma \\
\sqrt{2} \alpha & 0 & \sqrt{2} \gamma \\
\alpha & -\beta & -\gamma
\end{pmatrix} \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
4m \alpha^2 & 0 & 0 \\
0 & 2m \beta^2 & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 4m \gamma^2
\end{pmatrix} \\
&= I
\end{align*}
$$

需要取

$$\alpha = \pm \frac{1}{{2\sqrt m }},\beta = \pm \frac{1}{{\sqrt {2m} }},\gamma = \pm \frac{1}{{2\sqrt m }}$$

另一方面

$$
\begin{align*}
U^T K U &=
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha & \sqrt{2} \alpha & \alpha \\
\beta & 0 & -\beta \\
-\gamma & \sqrt{2} \gamma & -\gamma
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
2k & -k & 0 \\
-k & 2k & -k \\
0 & -k & 2k
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha & \beta & -\gamma \\
\sqrt{2} \alpha & 0 & \sqrt{2} \gamma \\
\alpha & -\beta & -\gamma
\end{pmatrix} \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
(8 - 4\sqrt{2}) \alpha^2 k & 0 & 0 \\
0 & 4 \beta^2 k & 0 \\
0 & 0 & (8 + 4\sqrt{2}) \gamma^2 k
\end{pmatrix} \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m} & 0 & 0 \\
0 & \frac{2k}{m} & 0 \\
0 & 0 & \frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}
\end{pmatrix} \\
&= \Lambda
\end{align*}
$$

此时有

$$
\begin{cases}
\vec{u}_1 &= \begin{pmatrix} \frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \\ \frac{1}{\sqrt{2m}} \\ \frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \end{pmatrix} \\
\vec{u}_2 &= \begin{pmatrix} \frac{1}{\sqrt{2m}} \\ 0 \\ -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2m}} \end{pmatrix} \\
\vec{u}_3 &= \begin{pmatrix} -\frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \\ \frac{1}{\sqrt{2m}} \\ -\frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \end{pmatrix}
\end{cases}
$$

div.data-content:
令$\vec y = U\vec \eta$, 代入

$$M\ddot {\vec y} + K \vec y = 0$$

有

$$MU\ddot {\vec \eta} + KU\vec \eta = 0$$

左乘$U^T$

$${U^T}MU\ddot {\vec \eta} + {U^T}KU\vec \eta = I\ddot {\vec \eta} + \Lambda \vec \eta = 0$$

即

$$
\begin{align*}
\ddot{\eta}_1 + \lambda_1 \eta_1 &= 0, \\
\ddot{\eta}_2 + \lambda_2 \eta_2 &= 0, \\
\ddot{\eta}_3 + \lambda_3 \eta_3 &= 0.
\end{align*}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 &= C_1 \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) + C_2 \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right), \\
\eta_2 &= C_3 \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right) + C_4 \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{2k}{m}} t \right), \\
\eta_3 &= C_5 \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) + C_6 \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right).
\end{cases}
$$

box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
知

$$U^TMU = I \Rightarrow U^{-1} = U^T M$$

有

$$
\begin{cases}
\begin{align*}
\vec{\eta}(0) &= U^{-1} \vec{y}(0)\\
&=U^T M \vec{y}(0) \\
&= \frac{\sqrt{m}}{2}
\begin{pmatrix}
1 & \sqrt{2} & 1 \\
\sqrt{2} & 0 & -\sqrt{2} \\
-1 & \sqrt{2} & -1
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
1 \\
0
\end{pmatrix} \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
\sqrt{\frac{m}{2}} \\
0 \\
\sqrt{\frac{m}{2}}
\end{pmatrix} \\
\end{align*} \\
\dot{\vec{\eta}}(0) = U^T M \dot{\vec{y}}(0) = \vec{0}
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$${C_2} = {C_3} = {C_4} = {C_6} = 0,{C_1} = {C_5} = \sqrt {\frac{m}{2}}$$

所以

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 = \sqrt{\frac{m}{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\
\eta_2 = 0 \\
\eta_3 = \sqrt{\frac{m}{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right)
\end{cases}
$$

可得

$$
\begin{pmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{pmatrix} =
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\
\frac{1}{2} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) + \frac{1}{2} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\
-\frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}} \cos \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right)
\end{pmatrix}
$$

$$

\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{\frac{m}{(4 - 2\sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 - \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) - \frac{1}{2}\sqrt{\frac{m}{(4 + 2\sqrt{2})k}} \sin \left( \sqrt{\frac{(2 + \sqrt{2})k}{m}} t \right) \\

\end{pmatrix}
\end{align*}
$$

div.data-content:
代入条件有:

$$
\begin{align*}
\begin{bmatrix}
2m & 0 & 0 \\
0 & 2m & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 2m
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y}_1 \\
\ddot{y}_2 \\
\ddot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix}
+
\begin{bmatrix}
3k & -k & 0 \\
-k & 2k & -k \\
0 & -k & 3k
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{bmatrix} =
\begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\end{align*}
$$

特征多项式

$$
\begin{align*}
\left| K - \lambda M \right| &=
\begin{vmatrix}
3k - 2\lambda m & -k & 0 \\
-k & 2k - 2\lambda m & -k \\
0 & -k & 3k - 2\lambda m
\end{vmatrix} \\
&= 12 k^3-38 \lambda k^2 m+32 \lambda ^2 k m^2-8 \lambda ^3 m^3 \\
&= 0
\end{align*}
$$

特征值

$$
\begin{cases}
\lambda_1 = \frac{k}{2m} \\
\lambda_2 = \frac{3k}{2m} \\
\lambda_3 = \frac{2k}{m}
\end{cases}
$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\omega_1 = \sqrt \frac{k}{2m} \\
\omega_2 = \sqrt \frac{3k}{2m} \\
\omega_3 = \sqrt \frac{2k}{m}
\end{cases}
$$

特征向量

$$
\begin{cases}
\vec{u}_1 &= \alpha \begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 2 \\ 1 \end{pmatrix} \\
\vec{u}_2 &= \beta \begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ -1 \end{pmatrix} \\
\vec{u}_3 &= \gamma \begin{pmatrix} -1 \\ 1 \\ -1 \end{pmatrix}
\end{cases}
$$
